{
  "stem": "25651.15",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he worked as a director and has made films.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Quite a tal-- I've seen some of his films.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He's made a film about Theresienstadt, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think he gave evidence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He told me that he gave evidence to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Tommy said, from our room, the [INAUDIBLE] party, we will stay down river at a different hotel, which is more secluded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you can't get there by car except for a big detour, and we're not going to have any television cameras.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And every morning I took a stroll down to my friends from [INAUDIBLE], whom I knew better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had a nice, sort of-- we were friends again, like we were in public school together in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And there was Karl Langer and Tommy Frankel and Paul Laupert and Otto Jacubowicz, myself--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Daniel was born in '56, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just over a year after we got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were married, and we were staying in St.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Annes-on-Sea.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was finishing my engineering apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was working on the P1 Lightning Fighter, and I could see that the future in the aircraft industry for a Jew, you know, amongst secret work in the Ministry of Defense was not the atmosphere for me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was married, and Eve says one evening-- I mean, we were using stuff, you know, not-- because we were young.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eve was only 18.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's says, I don't think I can get pregnant, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we tried, [LAUGHS] and, of course, bang, she got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then we didn't have any friends there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, we're going back to London, and I'm going to give up the aircraft industry.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
